飯。我去問男朋友，佢死都話無，咁我梗係信佢，之後仲走去鬧我朋友叫佢唔好亂作。<br />\n<br />\n佢再話原來我男朋友個日送完我搭車之後就送左我好朋友返屋企，仲同我好朋友喺後樓梯到搞左，最後秘密一齊咗。好多朋友都知，係得我一個唔知......<br />\n<br />\n之後去搵男朋友嘅一個兄弟確認，佢見到我係咁喊就同我講真有其事，仲要話係我好朋友勾引我男朋友在先......我真係接受唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知應該點去面對......</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/kong-goo-lo/hoxlong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fkong-goo-lo%2Fhoxlong&d=wBeSCwnTTd5wjbNQPqXIANtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bebb38cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/kong-goo-lo/hoxlong</a><br />\n<br />\n好長"},{"pid":"65fc70ab543ab95f9efd48b82ea83539ea57883a","tid":417380,"uid":415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:45:46.000Z","msg":"自己推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e000a9688cf9f0223b49591cb84b7c0dc565f6c8","tid":417380,"uid":415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"多謝俾正皮嘅巴/絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e74494e4a717fcb27a8d84bf51984174d6d6c3","tid":417380,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"正皮<br />\n笑到仆街"},{"pid":"a62142e7bfdb5497234c3fb977e3ef81007dd482","tid":417380,"uid":415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮<br />\n笑到仆街</blockquote><br />\n多謝你嘅正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/kong-goo-lo/jpsdpk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fkong-goo-lo%2Fjpsdpk&d=wBeSCwnTTd5wjbNQPqXIANtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=49d9ab2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/kong-goo-lo/jpsdpk</a>"},{"pid":"20b9aebfa9f5206aeba630b5efa8685966749ccd","tid":417380,"uid":415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:25:00.000Z","msg":"再推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}